quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  50,36,"Wakam ahlakna qablahum min qarnin humashaddu minhum batshan fanaqqaboo fee albiladi halmin mahees"
  50,37,"Inna fee thalika lathikraliman kana lahu qalbun aw alqa assamAAawahuwa shaheed"
  50,38,"Walaqad khalaqna assamawatiwal-arda wama baynahuma fee sittatiayyamin wama massana min lughoob"
  50,39,"Fasbir AAala mayaqooloona wasabbih bihamdi rabbika qabla tulooAAiashshamsi waqabla alghuroob"
  50,40,"Wamina allayli fasabbihhu waadbaraassujood"
  50,41,"WastamiAA yawma yunadi almunadimin makanin qareeb"
  50,42,"Yawma yasmaAAoona assayhatabilhaqqi thalika yawmu alkhurooj"
  50,43,"Inna nahnu nuhyeewanumeetu wa-ilayna almaseer"
  50,44,"Yawma tashaqqaqu al-ardu AAanhum siraAAanthalika hashrun AAalayna yaseer"
  50,45,"Nahnu aAAlamu bima yaqooloonawama anta AAalayhim bijabbarin fathakkir bilqur-animan yakhafu waAAeed"
  51,1,"Waththariyati tharwa"
  51,2,"Falhamilati wiqra"
  51,3,"Faljariyati yusra"
  51,4,"Falmuqassimati amra"
  51,5,"Innama tooAAadoona lasadiq"
  51,6,"Wa-inna addeena lawaqiAA"
